
Messages sent by the ECS to a Server nodes:
	INIT <metadata>
	START
	STOP
	SHUTDOWN
	LOCK_WRITE
	UNLOCK_WRITE
	MOVE_DATA <startIndex> <endIndex> <server>
	UPDATE <metadata>
	CONNECT
	DISCONNECT

Messages sent by a Server nodes to the ECS: 
	CONNECT_SUCCESS
	CONNECT_ERROR
	DISCONNECT_SUCCESS


Types of the arguments:
	INIT, START, STOP, etc: ECSStatusType
	<metadata>: InfrastructureMetadata
	<startIndex>, <endIndex>: BigInteger
	<server>: ServerData
